      "user_id": "U011U13BEPR",
      "user_label": "Chris Williams (U011U13BEPR)",
      "text": "Are we abandoning fog seals and seal coats because they are not black? The only application where I have heard this is important is for outdoor basketball and tennis courts. Without googling or searching the internet, can someone explain the difference between pavement preservation and pavement maintenance?",
