      "user_id": "U011U13BEPR",
      "user_label": "Chris Williams (U011U13BEPR)",
      "text": "Pavement preservation includes applying fog seals and seal coats sometimes the same year the pavement layer was constructed but certainly within 2 years. ",
      "subtype": null,
      "thread_ts": null,
      "edited_ts": null,
      "deleted": false,
      "attachments": []
    },
    {
      "ts": "1708793770.972689",
      "human_ts": "2024-02-24 10:56:10 CST",
      "user_id": "U011U13BEPR",
      "user_label": "Chris Williams (U011U13BEPR)",
      "text": "Let\u2019s do a simply field test and go spray Krylon paint on a faded asphalt pavement, a 1 foot strip across the entire lane and let\u2019s see what it looks like a few months later and continue to imagine what the customer thinks and if they would buy a pigment modified Vitala or Vitala+ fog seal/seal coat again.",
      "subtype": null,
      "thread_ts": null,
      "edited_ts": null,
      "deleted": false,
      "attachments": []
    },
    {
      "ts": "1708797318.493929",
      "human_ts": "2024-02-24 11:55:18 CST",
      "user_id": "U011U13BEPR",
      "user_label": "Chris Williams (U011U13BEPR)",
      "text": "Wednesday this week I drove to Omaha. Just west of Adair, Iowa my son engaged me on a conversation about the pavement being red.",
